sofiafitness.com";}i:20;a:11:{s:7:"keyword";s:34:"online chair based exercise course";s:4:"slug";s:34:"online-chair-based-exercise-course";s:5:"title";s:19:"Pin On Yoga Fitness";s:3:"alt";s:46:"https www pinterest com pin 494762709066389687";s:3:"url";s:76:"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/3f/2a/a7/3f2aa722b79dde1e7f90804052c66418.jpg";s:5:"thumb";s:90:"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSRoCungawg9b6wYGCktgDGf0c_e2OR-TiFeg";s:8:"filetype";s:3:"jpg";s:5:"width";i:8665;s:6:"height";i:4501;s:6:"source";s:49:"https://www.pinterest.com/pin/494762709066389687/";s:6:"domain";s:17:"www.pinterest.com";}}s:9:"sentences";a:56:{i:0;s:286:"The LifeDock Chair Based Exercise Instructor Training course is a fully accredited level 2 qualification and has been designed for those who understand the value and rewards of bringing physical activity and exercise to older people and adults with physical andor learning disabilities.";i:1;s:51:"Chair-based exercise instructor 2020 22800 inc VAT.";i:2;s:67:"Online quiz that you will need to gain 18 marks out of 25 marks 70.";i:3;s:66:"You may reattempt the quiz as many times as necessary if required.";i:4;s:44:"Online access will be provided for one year.";i:5;s:87:"This will allow you time to complete the course and revisit the training material even.";i:6;s:98:"Chair based exercise classes are well suited to older adults and people with mobility limitations.";i:7;s:140:"They aim to increase stamina flexibility and coordination containing many elements of a traditional fitness class just in a seated position.";i:8;s:117:"The course will develop your knowledge understanding and skills to effectively deliver chair-based exercise sessions.";i:9;s:164:"Specifically you will learn about the values and principles of adult social care and the effects that ageing disability and inactivity can have on the body systems.";i:10;s:137:"This Seated Exercise Activity Instructor course package is a very cost-effective way to kick-start running chair-based exercise sessions.";i:11;s:118:"You will be able to run the traditional chair-based exercise classes using resistance bands with the added benefit of.";i:12;s:44:"Gentle Chair Based Exercise Leader Training.";i:13;s:126:"A practical certified course that teaches you how to create and deliver a chair based exercise session for those in your care.";i:14;s:107:"The course teaches you which exercises are suitable for those with the chronic conditions listed below and.";i:15;s:158:"This chair based exercise routine is ideal for people who are concerned about their ability to stand while exercising so we do the whole routine sitting down.";i:16;s:126:"Youll be surprised at how much you can work your whole body from a chair and this can be done in the comfort of your own home.";i:17;s:41:"Chair-Based Exercise Leader Course Dates.";i:18;s:67:"If there are no suitable dates below please contact the LLT office.";i:19;s:86:"If there is enough interest in a geographical area we will look to instigate a course.";i:20;s:25:"Number of Learning Hours.";i:21;s:52:"L2 Chair-based Exercise Instructor endorsed- Online.";i:22;s:37:"Accredited by a Professional Body eg.";i:23;s:27:"HSE CIEH FSA Certification.";i:24;s:57:"Certificate of Achievement Assessed by Provider Category.";i:25;s:23:"Seated Gentle Exercise.";i:26;s:68:"Chair One Fitness a comprehensive chair-based dance fitness program.";i:27;s:60:"You can become an instructor or enjoy or on-demand workouts.";i:28;s:97:"Our program was created for individuals who have complications standing during a fitness regimen.";i:29;s:107:"This includes senior citizens people with balance deficits injuries disabilities or suffering from obesity.";i:30;s:117:"The course is designed for health care professionals wishing to deliver chair-based exercise to frailer older people.";i:31;s:132:"It is also appropriate for qualified exercise teachers and those holding an NVQ in Exercise and Fitness or equivalent qualification.";i:32;s:190:"Courses for Activity Co-Ordinators Below is a list of different courses we offer specifically for activity co-ordinators and for people who provide activities in care and community settings.";i:33;s:136:"This may include residential homes nursing homes sheltered housing supported living independent living day centres and community groups.";i:34;s:97:"Jane Mackenzie is also fully qualified in chair-based exercise and exercise with diabled clients.";i:35;s:111:"In response to requests from community groups Jane currently offers chair-based exercise videos free of charge.";i:36;s:133:"Includes instructional video on how to get in and out of a chair correctly in order to strengthen the legs and preserve good posture.";i:37;s:111:"This course is available for people who wish to deliver chair-based exercise sessions for frailer older people.";i:38;s:61:"The main physiological changes that occur to the ageing body.";i:39;s:73:"Screening tests used to determine readiness to exercise for older people.";i:40;s:36:"Referral routes available for older.";i:41;s:171:"Chair based-exercise is a great way for anyone with AKU to participate in aerobic exercise even if you have reduced mobility in the joints or have had a joint replacement.";i:42;s:65:"All the exercises have adaptations depending on your own ability.";i:43;s:29:"Download the FREE HASfit app.";i:44;s:59:"Use a chair with a flat firm backrest and a flat firm seat.";i:45;s:35:"The class is about 30 minutes long.";i:46;s:127:"Regular pilates practice can help improve posture muscle tone balance and joint mobility as well as relieve stress and tension.";i:47;s:42:"These fitness videos have been created by.";i:48;s:163:"Amac already provide Chair-based Exercise courses to Local Authorities and care homes and the option to complete the qualification online has been welcomed by all.";i:49;s:64:"Studies can be completed independantly anywhere and at any time.";i:50;s:107:"Amacs bespoke e-learning resources include animations and videos which keep content engaging and inspiring.";i:51;s:64:"Chair Based Exercises Level 2 Accredited qualification Cohort 2.";i:52;s:124:"This course is delivered over four sessions 28th 30th June and 5th7th July 2021 and all sessions must be attended TCs apply.";i:53;s:101:"This course has a coursework element which must be completed in order to adhere the course TCs apply.";i:54;s:55:"One of our programmes for the older less mobile person.";i:55;s:99:"This is also an ideal class for anyone wishing to rehabilitate themselves after any majopr surgery.";}}